<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A9201001001">
<title>
Auto-On Headlight System (If Equipped)
</title>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
The auto-on headlight system is a system to control the automatic ON / OFF of headlight, clearance lights, tail lights, license plate lights and adjust interior illumination optimally according to ambient brightness when lighting switch is in AUTO position.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
BCM controls the operation of the auto-on headlight system based on light intensity signals from auto-on headlight sensor.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
With the ignition in “ON” and the lighting switch in “AUTO”, BCM controls operation of the headlights, clearance lights, tail lights and license plate lights in the following patterns according to the outside light condition.
