<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A9201001002">
<title>
DRL System (If Equipped)
</title>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
The DRL system consists of the DRL control module (ignition switch model) or BCM (keyless push start model), lighting switch, tail lights, clearance lights, license plate lights, headlights and generator.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
When the engine is running and the lighting switch is set to “OFF”, the DRL control module (ignition switch model) or BCM (keyless push start model) causes the headlight low beams to light at dimmed brightness.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
